***definitions***
- :Account: is a record of a user's account.

***implementation reqs***
- A user can register an :Account:.
- A user can login to an :Account:.
- A user can logout from an :Account:.
- A user can view their :Account:.
- A user can edit their :Account:.
- A user can delete their :Account:.
- When a user logs or registers, the :App: should generate a :AccessToken: for the user.
- :Authentication: should be applied to all CRUD endpoints for :Account: objects.

***functional specs***
- Implement a POST /register endpoint that allows a user to register an :Account:.
- Implement a POST /login endpoint that allows a user to login to an :Account:.
- Implement a POST /logout endpoint that allows a user to logout from an :Account:.

- Implement CRUD endpoints for :Account: objects.
